SHPB DATA PROCESSOR¶

Version 1.1 updated at Nov.11 2019¶

Download: https://pan.baidu.com/s/1anFX_XiXWydbON9MfcF2JA c02a

New features:¶

  1. Add statusbar which shows the name of the active file.
  1. In the plot-original-waveform module, you can choose the type of input data(time-strain or time-voltage).
  1. Add export data button in the align-wave module.
  1. More aspects showed in the result module.
  1. Add dialog after exporting data successfully.
